dct_title_s: Map of the Minnesota Arrowhead country and central Canada from Winnipeg to the Nipigon
dct_description_sm: Panel title: Minnesota Arrowhead.; Includes two insets of illustrations; one in upper left center, and one at lower left with title: Iron ore mining in the Arrowhead country.; Verso of map includes illustrations, text describing the Arrowhead Region, and map with title: Road map of the Minnesota Arrowhead country. Scale [approximately 1:2,250,000].
55 x 85 centimeters, on sheet 61 x 92 centimeters
dct_publisher_sm: Issued by the Minnesota Arrowhead Association (Duluth,  Minn), 1926
